    <title>Typora基础</title>
    <link href="/2024/02/22/Typora%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/"/>
    <url>/2024/02/22/Typora%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>第一遍博客，先记录Typora的学习过程，便于更熟悉地使用Typora语法来写后面的博客，使用Typora在于其支持Markdown和富文本，而且实时渲染用起来感觉确实要比其他舒服很多。下面总结了Typora使用中常见的用法。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="typora基础">Typora基础</h2><h4 id="目录">目录</h4><p>使用 <code>[TOC]</code> 显示为目录</p><h4 id="标题">标题</h4><p>一共六级标题，使用标题显示在目录中</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-section"># 一级标题(Ctrl+1)</span><br><span class="hljs-section">## 二级标题(Ctrl+2)</span><br><span class="hljs-section">### 三级标题(Ctrl+3)</span><br><span class="hljs-section">#### 四级标题(Ctrl+4)</span><br><span class="hljs-section">##### 五级标题(Ctrl+5)</span><br><span class="hljs-section">###### 六级标题(Ctrl+6)</span><br>正文内容快捷键(Ctrl+0)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="下划线">下划线</h4><p>预览效果：<u>内容</u></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">使用 <span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">u</span>&gt;</span></span>内容<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br>或快捷键 (Ctrl+U)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="删除线">删除线</h4><p>预览效果：<del>内容</del></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">使用 一对 ~~ 括住删除内容<br><br>或快捷键 (Alt+Shift+5)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="字体加粗">字体加粗</h4><p>预览效果：<strong>内容</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">使用 一对 ** 括住加粗内容<br>或快捷键 (Ctrl+B)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="字体倾斜">字体倾斜</h4><p>预览效果：<em>内容</em></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">使用 一对 * 括住倾斜内容<br>或快捷键 (Ctrl+I)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="代码区域">代码区域</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">使用 <span class="hljs-code">``` 回车即可出现当前框代码框效果</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="链接">链接</h4><p>预览效果：</p><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com/"class="uri">https://www.baidu.com/</a></p><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com/">百度</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">使用 &lt; &gt; 括住网址<br>或<br>[<span class="hljs-string">文字</span>](<span class="hljs-link">网址</span>)<br>快捷键 (Ctrl+K)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用<strong>Ctrl+鼠标左键</strong>点击访问</p><p>链接的其他用途还有<strong>打开本地文件</strong>，<strong>页内跳转</strong></p><p>如<code>[打开本地文件](./Typora基础.md)</code>、<code>[页内跳转](####目录)</code></p><p>注意：<code>.</code>表示当前目录，<code>..</code>则表示上一级目录；进行页内跳转时#后面不需要加空格</p><h4 id="表格">表格</h4><p>预览效果：</p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th>表头</th><th>表头</th><th>表头</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">使用<br>|表头|表头|表头|<br>或快捷键 (Ctrl+T)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="列表">列表</h4><h5 id="任务列表">1. 任务列表</h5><p>预览效果：</p><ul class="task-list"><li><label><input type="checkbox" />事项1</label></li><li><label><input type="checkbox" checked="" />事项2</label></li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> [ ] 事项1<br><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> [ ] 事项2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="无序列表">2. 无序列表</h5><p>预览效果：</p><ul><li>事项</li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-bullet">+</span> 或 - 或 * 加空格<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="有序列表">3. 有序列表</h5><p>预览效果：</p><ol type="1"><li>java</li><li>python<ol type="1"><li>python</li></ol></li></ol><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-bullet">1.</span> 加空格<br>多级有序列表使用tab键<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="分割线">分割线</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-strong">*** 或 ---</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="引用">引用</h4><p>预览效果：</p><blockquote><p>引用内容</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; 空格</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="插入图片">插入图片</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">可将本地图片直接拖进来<br>或以下形式<br>![<span class="hljs-string">本地图片</span>](<span class="hljs-link">./本地图片.png</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">网络图片</span>](<span class="hljs-link">网络图片地址</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果使用本地图片的方式会十分麻烦，图片需要根据相对路径随文件一起移动才能正常显示，只适合在图片较少或没有发布需求时使用。一般推荐使用图床将本地图片托管到网络，使用图片的网络地址。</p><p>使用<ahref="https://picgo.github.io/PicGo-Doc/">PicGo</a>上传图片，安装PicGo后配置，这里使用Git保存图片，国内Gitee相对Github访问速度快，因此这里使用Gitee保存图片，以下是PicGo下载后配置的流程。</p><h5 id="下载gitee插件">1. 下载gitee插件</h5><p>在PicGo插件设置搜索安装如下插件</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/e-year/images/raw/master/img/image-20240220124337530.png" alt="image-20240220124337530" style="zoom: 50%;" /></p><h5 id="创建gitee仓库用于存储图片">2. 创建gitee仓库用于存储图片</h5><p>新建仓库过程省略，任意开源的仓库都可用于存储图片</p><p>还需要用到私人令牌，登录Gitee账户后，点击个人头像进入设置，在左侧进入私人令牌，生成新令牌。之后自行填写描述并勾选权限，点击提交，输入密码验证即可。注意复制保留生成的token。</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/e-year/images/raw/master/img/image-20240220192907942.png" alt="image-20240220192907942" style="zoom: 33%;" /></p><h5 id="在图床设置填好gitee仓库信息以及私人令牌token">3.在图床设置填好Gitee仓库信息以及私人令牌token</h5><p><img src="https://gitee.com/e-year/images/raw/master/img/image-20240220121839556.png" alt="image-20240220121839556" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><h5 id="在上传区测试图片能否正常上传">4.在上传区测试图片能否正常上传</h5><p><img src="https://gitee.com/e-year/images/raw/master/img/image-20240220125044095.png" alt="image-20240220125044095" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><ol start="5" type="1"><li><h5id="点击typora界面左上角-文件-的偏好设置中设置上传服务设定选择picgoapp并填入本地picgo.exe位置验证图片在typora是否正常上传">点击Typora界面左上角文件的偏好设置中，设置上传服务设定，选择PicGo(app)并填入本地PicGo.exe位置，验证图片在Typora是否正常上传</h5></li></ol><p><img src="https://gitee.com/e-year/images/raw/master/img/image-20240220125405883.png" alt="image-20240220125405883" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p>​ <strong>如果图片上传错误</strong></p><ol type="1"><li>检查PicGo设置server中端口是否与Typora中一致</li></ol><figure><imgsrc="https://gitee.com/e-year/images/raw/master/img/202402202343510.png"alt="image-20240220234259721" /><figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20240220234259721</figcaption></figure><ol start="2" type="1"><li>将时间戳重命名打开，在上传成功过的情况下，如果上传失败，可能就是因为上传了同名文件</li></ol><figure><imgsrc="https://gitee.com/e-year/images/raw/master/img/202402202344804.png"alt="image-20240220234439324" /><figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20240220234439324</figcaption></figure><p>在平时使用过程可先将图片复制在文件中，再右键上传图片和缩放图片即可快速编辑</p><h4 id="数学表达式">数学表达式</h4><h5 id="插入数学公式">1. 插入数学公式</h5><p>输入<code>$$</code>+<code>Enter</code>或是 (Ctrl+Shift+M)创建一个数学公式块</p><p>行内公式可使用<code>$</code>包裹书写的公式，该功能需要在偏好设置中勾选上markdown扩展语法，全部勾上后可正常使用包括公式<code>$</code>、下标<code>~</code>、上标<code>^</code>、高亮<code>==</code>的功能（都是使用符号包裹文本）。</p><h5 id="常见数学符号">2. 常见数学符号</h5><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">效果</th><th style="text-align: center;">公式</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\sqrt{x}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\sqrt{2}</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\sqrt[3]{4}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\sqrt[3]{4}</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\vec{a}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\vec{a}</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\overrightarrow{AB}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\overrightarrow{AB}</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\overleftarrow{AB}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\overleftarrow{AB}</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\frac{1}{2}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\frac{1}{2}</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\int_{1}^{2}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\int_{1}^{2}</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\sum_{i=1}^{10}x_i\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\sum_{i=1}^{10}x_i</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\prod_{i=1}^{10}x_i\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\prod_{i=1}^{10}x_i</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\partial\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\partial</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\ge\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\ge</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\le\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\le</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\ne\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\ne</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\times\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\times</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\div\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\div</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\lbrace\rbrace\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\lbrace\rbrace</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(a \cdotb\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">a \cdot b</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(a \astb\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">a \ast b</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\sin(x)\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\sin(x)</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\cos(x)\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\cos(x)</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\tan(x)\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\tan(x)</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(\log_210\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\log_2 10</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\ln2\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\ln2</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\infty\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\infty</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\hat{a}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\hat{a}</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\overline{xyz}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\overline{xyz}</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(lim{n\rightarrow+\infty}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">lim{n\rightarrow+\infty}</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\sum^{x\to\infty}_{y\to 0}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\sum^{x\to\infty}_{y\to 0}</td></tr></tbody></table><h5 id="矩阵">3. 矩阵</h5><ol type="1"><li>无括号</li></ol><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">\left|\begin&#123;matrix&#125;<br>1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 \\\<br>4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6<br>\end&#123;matrix&#125;\right|<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span class="math display">\[\begin{matrix}1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3\\\4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6\end{matrix}\]</span></p><ol start="2" type="1"><li>矩阵</li></ol><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\left</span>[<span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span>&#123;matrix&#125;<br>1 <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> 2 <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> 3 <span class="hljs-keyword">\\</span><span class="hljs-keyword">\</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword"></span>4 <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> 5 <span class="hljs-built_in">&amp;</span> 6<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span>&#123;matrix&#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">\right</span>]<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span class="math display">\[\left[\begin{matrix}1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3\\\4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6\end{matrix}\right]\]</span></p><ol start="3" type="1"><li>行列式</li></ol><figure class="highlight 1c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs 1c">\left<span class="hljs-string">|\begin&#123;matrix&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-meta">&amp; 2 &amp; 3\\\</span><br><span class="hljs-number">4</span> <span class="hljs-meta">&amp; 5 &amp; 6</span><br>\end&#123;matrix&#125;\right<span class="hljs-string">|</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span class="math display">\[\left|\begin{matrix}1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3\\4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6\end{matrix}\right|\]</span></p><p>注意：在使用hexo写博客时，使用<code>\\</code>换行会出现无法显示的问题，因为渲染引擎会把<code>\\</code>渲染成<code>\</code>，再交给mathjax渲染公式，不修改配置情况下需要多加一个<code>\</code>写成<code>\\\</code>才能正常显示。</p><h5 id="方程组">4. 方程组</h5><p>示例： <span class="math display">\[\begin{equation}\left\{             \begin{array}{lr}             x=\dfrac{3\pi}{2}(1+2t)\cos(\dfrac{3\pi}{2}(1+2t)),   \\\             y=s, &amp; 0\leq s\leq L,|t|\leq1.\\\             z=\dfrac{3\pi}{2}(1+2t)\sin(\dfrac{3\pi}{2}(1+2t)),                \end{array}\right.\end{equation}\]</span></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">源代码如下：<br>\begin&#123;equation&#125;<br>\left\&#123;<br><span class="hljs-code">             \begin&#123;array&#125;&#123;lr&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-code">             x=\dfrac&#123;3\pi&#125;&#123;2&#125;(1+2t)\cos(\dfrac&#123;3\pi&#125;&#123;2&#125;(1+2t)),   \\\</span><br><span class="hljs-code">             y=s, &amp; 0\leq s\leq L,|t|\leq1.\\\</span><br><span class="hljs-code">             z=\dfrac&#123;3\pi&#125;&#123;2&#125;(1+2t)\sin(\dfrac&#123;3\pi&#125;&#123;2&#125;(1+2t)),   </span><br><span class="hljs-code">             \end&#123;array&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-code">\right.</span><br><span class="hljs-code">\end&#123;equation&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>\begin&#123;equation&#125;</code>和<code>\end&#123;equation&#125;</code>表示之间内容为方程组</li><li><code>\left\&#123;</code>表示在方程组左边加<code>&#123;</code>,<code>\right.</code>表示在右边加<code>.</code></li><li><code>\begin&#123;array&#125;</code>和<code>\end&#123;array&#125;</code>表示之间内容为数组或矩阵，可见中间内容也用<code>&amp;</code>分割开来表示数组的各个元素和<code>\\</code>表示换行</li><li><code>&#123;lr&#125;</code>表示有两列，第一列<code>l</code>表示值靠左，第二列<code>r</code>表示值靠右，而<code>c</code>则表示值居中</li></ul><h5 id="希腊字母">5. 希腊字母</h5><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">大写字母</th><th style="text-align: center;">语法</th><th style="text-align: center;">小写字母</th><th style="text-align: center;">语法</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(A\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">A</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\alpha\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\alpha</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(B\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">B</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\beta\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\beta</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Gamma\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Gamma</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\gamma\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\gamma</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Delta\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Delta</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\delta\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\delta</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(E\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">E</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\epsilon\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\epsilon</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(Z\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">Z</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\zeta\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\zeta</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(H\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">H</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\eta\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\eta</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Theta\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Theta</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\theta\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\theta</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Lambda\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Lambda</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\lambda\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\lambda</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\mu\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\mu</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\xi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\xi</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Xi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Xi</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\omicron\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\omicron</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Pi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Pi</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\pi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\pi</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\rho\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\rho</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Sigma\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Sigma</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\sigma\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\sigma</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Upsilon\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Upsilon</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(T\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">T</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\tau\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\tau</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Phi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Phi</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\phi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\phi</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(X\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">X</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\chi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\chi</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Psi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Psi</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\psi\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\psi</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\Omega\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\Omega</td><td style="text-align: center;"><spanclass="math inline">\(\omega\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">\omega</td></tr></tbody></table><p>更多：<ahref="https://blog.csdn.net/wait_for_eva/article/details/84307306">typora-数字符号</a></p><h4 id="图表">图表</h4><p>使用Mermaid绘制画图，输入```<code>mermaid</code>回车得到空白图</p><p><strong>1. 流程图</strong></p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css">graph <span class="hljs-selector-tag">TD</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-selector-tag">A</span>--&gt;<span class="hljs-selector-tag">B</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-selector-tag">A</span>--&gt;C;<br>    <span class="hljs-selector-tag">B</span>--&gt;D;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code class=" mermaid">graph TD;    A--&gt;B;    A--&gt;C;    B--&gt;D;</code></pre><p><strong>2. 时序图</strong></p><figure class="highlight coq"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs coq">sequenceDiagram<br>    Alice-&gt;&gt;John: Hello John, how are you?<br>    Note <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span> of Alice: Alice thinks<br>Note <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span> of Alice: Alice thinks<br>Note <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span> of John: Bob thinks<br>Note <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span> of John: Bob thinks<br>    John--&gt;&gt;Alice: Great!<br>其中-&gt;&gt;表示实线，--&gt;&gt;表示虚线，note <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>/<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span> of 表示备注<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code class=" mermaid">sequenceDiagram    Alice-&gt;&gt;John: Hello John, how are you?    Note left of Alice: Alice thinksNote right of Alice: Alice thinksNote left of John: Bob thinksNote right of John: Bob thinks    John--&gt;&gt;Alice: Great!</code></pre><p><strong>3. 状态图</strong></p><figure class="highlight pf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pf"><span class="hljs-keyword">state</span>Diagram<br>    [*] --&gt; s1<br>    s1 --&gt; [*]<br>[*]表示开始结束<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code class=" mermaid">stateDiagram    [*] --&gt; s1    s1 --&gt; [*]</code></pre><p><strong>4. 类图</strong></p><figure class="highlight isbl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs isbl"><span class="hljs-variable">classDiagram</span><br>      <span class="hljs-variable">Animal</span> &lt;|-- <span class="hljs-variable">Duck</span><br>      <span class="hljs-variable">Animal</span> &lt;|-- <span class="hljs-variable">Fish</span><br>      <span class="hljs-variable">Animal</span> &lt;|-- <span class="hljs-variable">Zebra</span><br>      <span class="hljs-variable">Animal</span> : +<span class="hljs-variable">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">age</span><br>      <span class="hljs-variable">Animal</span> : +<span class="hljs-variable">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">gender</span><br>      <span class="hljs-variable">Animal</span>: +<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">isMammal</span>()</span><br>      <span class="hljs-variable">Animal</span>: +<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">mate</span>()</span><br>      <span class="hljs-variable">class</span> <span class="hljs-variable">Duck</span>&#123;<br>          +<span class="hljs-variable">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">beakColor</span><br>          +<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">swim</span>()</span><br>          +<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">quack</span>()</span><br>      &#125;<br>      <span class="hljs-variable">class</span> <span class="hljs-variable">Fish</span>&#123;<br>          -<span class="hljs-variable">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">sizeInFeet</span><br>          -<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">canEat</span>()</span><br>      &#125;<br>      <span class="hljs-variable">class</span> <span class="hljs-variable">Zebra</span>&#123;<br>          +<span class="hljs-variable">bool</span> <span class="hljs-variable">is_wild</span><br>          +<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">run</span>()</span><br>      &#125;<br>&lt;|--表示继承，+表示<span class="hljs-variable">public</span>，-表示<span class="hljs-variable">private</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code class=" mermaid">classDiagram      Animal &lt;|-- Duck      Animal &lt;|-- Fish      Animal &lt;|-- Zebra      Animal : +int age      Animal : +String gender      Animal: +isMammal()      Animal: +mate()      class Duck&#123;          +String beakColor          +swim()          +quack()      &#125;      class Fish&#123;          -int sizeInFeet          -canEat()      &#125;      class Zebra&#123;          +bool is_wild          +run()      &#125;</code></pre><p><strong>5. 甘特图</strong></p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">gantt</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">title</span> 工作计划<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">dateFormat</span>  YYYY-MM-DD<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">section</span> Section<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">A</span> task           :a1, <span class="hljs-number">2020</span>-<span class="hljs-number">01</span>-<span class="hljs-number">01</span>, <span class="hljs-number">30</span>d<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">Another</span> task     :after a1  , <span class="hljs-number">20</span>d<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">section</span> Another<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">Task</span> in sec      :<span class="hljs-number">2020</span>-<span class="hljs-number">01</span>-<span class="hljs-number">12</span>  , <span class="hljs-number">12</span>d<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">another</span> task      : <span class="hljs-number">24</span>d<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code class=" mermaid">gantt    title 工作计划    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD    section Section    A task           :a1, 2020-01-01, 30d    Another task     :after a1  , 20d    section Another    Task in sec      :2020-01-12  , 12d    another task      : 24d</code></pre><p><strong>6. 饼图</strong></p><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ada">pie<br>    title Key elements <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> Product X<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Calcium&quot;</span> : 42.96<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Potassium&quot;</span> : 50.05<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Magnesium&quot;</span> : 10.01<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Iron&quot;</span> :  5<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code class=" mermaid">pie    title Key elements in Product X    &quot;Calcium&quot; : 42.96    &quot;Potassium&quot; : 50.05    &quot;Magnesium&quot; : 10.01    &quot;Iron&quot; :  5</code></pre><p>更多参考：<ahref="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43775143/article/details/106212765">使用Typora绘制图(表)_draw-diagrams-with-markdown-CSDN博客</a></p><h4 id="html">HTML</h4><p>可使用html来设置markdown不支持的格式，如文本颜色、添加视频、按钮等，由于html的内容还不熟悉，之后再进行完善。</p><blockquote><p>参考链接：</p><p>[1] Typora使用教程：<ahref="https://www.cnblogs.com/powerwu/articles/16324814.html#12_Typora_17"class="uri">https://www.cnblogs.com/powerwu/articles/16324814.html#12_Typora_17</a></p><p>[2] Typora v13.8 激活教程：<a href="http://www.itmind.net/85931.html"class="uri">http://www.itmind.net/85931.html</a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
